# application

This is code for a core banking application. The first use case covered in bitcoin backed lending.

This github repository is a monorepo. 

The backend is in rust. The frontend is in next js.

During local dev, Docker and Docker compose is being used.

Useful commands to run are in the Makefile.

The ledger is being handle by Cala, another rust crate. It maintain the list of all transactions and provide double entry bookkeeping ledger with strong consistency guarantees through custom templates